description:
This course is all about learning Excel in a practical way with the help of real time working examples.

This course has been made in length keeping in mind the various options and features of Excel and real time examples are demonstrated hands so that one has a clear working knowledge on Excel.

The entire course has been broken down into 14 Sections comprising of 78 tutorial videos giving a clear picture on the various functions of Excel discussed in this course.
title: Excel Learning Made Easy
